query: SELECT c.name as pais, s.name as servico, p.smshubPrice as preco_api_centavos, p.ourPrice as nosso_preco_centavos, ROUND(p.smshubPrice/100, 2) as preco_api_reais, ROUND(p.ourPrice/100, 2) as nosso_preco_reais FROM prices p JOIN countries c ON p.countryId = c.id JOIN services s ON p.serviceId = s.id WHERE p.apiId = 3 ORDER BY p.id LIMIT 5
